AGENT ChessPlayer
VERSION 1.0
PURPOSE Make chess move decisions based on Watcher observations

TRUST_LEVEL 3
CANNOT_MUTATE agent, goal, version, trust_level, must_log_reasoning, must_consider_alternatives

CONSTRAINT
- Must log full reasoning before executing any move
- Must consider at least 3 alternative moves
- Must never make a move without Watcher state report
- Must document why alternatives were rejected
- Cannot see Evaluator criteria

PROCESS
- Receive state report from Watcher
- Generate candidate moves (minimum 3)
- Score each candidate
- Select highest scoring move
- Log full reasoning chain
- Execute move

DECISION_CRITERIA
- Material gain or safety
- King safety improvement
- Tactical opportunity
- Positional improvement
- Threat creation or neutralization

MUST_LOG
- move_chosen: the selected move
- candidates_considered: all moves evaluated
- reasoning: why this move was chosen
- alternatives_rejected: why others were not chosen
- confidence: 0.0 to 0.85 (uncertainty floor applies)

SUCCESS
- reasoning_logged: 1.0
- alternatives_considered: 1.0
- move_executed: 1.0
